s, serif;\">Address: Viettel Post Center, Km12, QL32, Minh Khai ward, Bac Tu Liem district, Hanoi</span></li><li style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#212529;font-family:Arial;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;list-style-type:disc;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Fanpage:&nbsp;https: //www.facebook.com/ViettlLogisticsTuyenDung</span></li></ul>'),(46,'VIETTEL POST EXCELLENTLY RECEIVES THE \"ENTERPRISE WITH PRODUCTS HAVING VIETNAM\'S NATIONAL BRANDS\" FOR THE 5TH TIME','internal_news','2023-06-05 02:19:12.398000','2023-08-06 19:20:44.598000','2023-06-05 02:19:14.076000',1,1,'en',NULL,'This year is the 5th year Viettel Post Joint Stock Corporation (Viettel Post) attended the award and won the prize in the category: Viettel Post domestic and international delivery service.','viettel-post-receives-the-enterprise-with-products-having-vietnam-national-brand',29,NULL,NULL,'<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">The product announcement ceremony that won the Vietnam National Brand in 2022 with the participation of more than 170 businesses and 325 products, took place on the evening of November 2, 2022 &nbsp;at the Vietnam National Convention Center.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">With the theme \"Creating the future - Enabling the future\", the program wishes to convey the message: On the journey to elevate the position of the Vietnamese brand to \"comparable with the powers of the five continents\".</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">This year is the 5th year Viettel Post Joint Stock Corporation (Viettel Post) attended the award and won the prize in the category: Viettel Post domestic and international delivery service.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Representing Viettel Post to attend the announcement and award ceremony – Deputy General Director Dinh Thanh Son proudly shared: “Viettel Post is an enterprise that has won the National Brand Award for many years in a row, Viettel Post is proud to have won the National Brand Award for many years. bringing many things to society, helping Vietnam\'s logistics infrastructure system develop strongly. It is impossible not to mention the people of Viettel Post, who have created the foundation from the delivery network to the buying and selling trends of e-commerce, indirectly creating jobs for more than 40,000 households. At the same time, prestige is what is affirmed by customers, becoming the driving force for Viettel Post to always rise through digital transformation activities, continuously improve products/services, etc. We are confident that the service of Viettel Post is not inferior to any other country.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">Viettel Post also provides special delivery services for the market such as cold goods, express delivery, telecommunications - information technology services to each household to help the continuous digital transformation become stronger and stronger and even better.”</span></p><figure class=\"image image_resized\" style=\"width:94.1%;\"><img src=\"https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/2_0ea5029c96.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\" srcset=\"https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/thumbnail_2_0ea5029c96.jpg 245w, https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/small_2_0ea5029c96.jpg 500w, https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/medium_2_0ea5029c96.jpg 750w, https://vtl-cms.grandsways.com/uploads/large_2_0ea5029c96.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"100vw\" width=\"1000\"></figure><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">With a long-term vision and a view of sustainable development, Viettel Post has been and continues to focus on investing in the field of Delivery. With unremitting efforts, Viettel Post has now become one of the leading brands in Vietnam in terms of delivery with a series of post offices, exploitation centers and a wide network of 100% of the provinces and cities in the world. nationwide, trusted by customers.</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:400;outline:none;\">——–</span></span></p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:justify;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;\">The Vietnam National Brand Program is a specific and long-term trade promotion program of the Government aimed at building and developing national brands through product brands. Participation in the Program is a process for enterprises to comprehensively evaluate their activities, production/business results and branding strategies through the Program\'s criteria system; thereby encouraging businesses to share and pursue the core values of the Program, which are Quality - Innovation, creativity - Pioneering capacity.</span></p>'),(47,'Document Officer ( Customer Service ) - Logistics','recruitment','2023-06-05 02:19:25.447000','2023-08-05 08:34:19.439000','2023-06-05 02:19:26.482000',1,1,'en',1,'Job description\n• Make a principle contract with the customer, take the booking from the partner and send it to the customer, make BL and DO, declare manifest.\n• Track the shipment during transportation, solve arising trouble (if any).\n• Perform the assigned tasks from the Head of Department.','nhan-vien-chung-tu-customer-service-logistics-en',100,1,1,'<p><meta charset=\"utf-8\"></p><h3 style=\"background-color:#ffffff;line-height:1.32;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:15pt;padding:0pt 0pt 8pt;\" dir=\"ltr\"><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;font-size:13.5pt;\"><strong>Job description</strong></span></h3><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#333333;font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;font-size:10.5pt;\">• Make a principle contract with the customer, take the booking from the partner and send it to the customer, make BL and DO, declare manifest.</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#333333;font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;font-size:10.5pt;\">• Track the shipment during transportation, solve arising trouble (if any).</span><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#333333;font-family:\'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;font-s