hỉ website https://viettelpost.com.vn/ được đăng ký tại Bộ Công Thương nhằm mục đích cung cấp cho Khách hàng dịch vụ vận chuyển hàng hóa nhanh chóng và tiện lợi.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Trước khi đăng ký và sử dụng dịch vụ của Viettel Post, mong Quý khách vui lòng đọc kỹ các điều khoản sử dụng. Các điều khoản và điều kiện này được áp dụng cho việc sử dụng dịch vụ cũng như tất cả các thông tin, chính sách được cung cấp cho khách hàng trên ứng dụng và website của Viettel Post.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Thủ tục gửi bưu gửi</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Mở bưu gửi để giao dịch viên kiểm tra nội dung, chứng từ đi kèm</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Gói bọc bưu gửi theo quy định của Bưu chính Viettel (VTP), cân, niêm phong, đối chiếu cước phí với bảng giá và gửi kèm đầy đủ hóa đơn, chứng từ.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Điền đầy đủ thông tin, ký, ghi rõ họ tên vào mặt trước và mặt sau phiếu gửi.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Lưu liên 3 phiếu gửi.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Quyền của Người gửi</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Được Viettel Post cung cấp đầy đủ thông tin liên quan đến toàn bộ quy trình cung ứng Dịch vụ.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Được Viettel Post đảm bảo bí mật thông tin, an toàn đối với Bưu gửi trong toàn quá trình giao hàng theo qui định của pháp luật.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Được Viettel Post giải quyết khiếu nại, được giải quyết thỏa đáng về Dịch vụ cung ứng đã sử dụng. – Được Viettel Post bồi thường thiệt hại tùy theo thực tế từng trường hợp.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Nghĩa vụ của Người gửi</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Thực hiện việc đối soát cước phí Dịch vụ đảm bảo đúng thời hạn.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Không gửi Bưu gửi chưa được lưu thông trên thị trường, hàng cấm, hàng hạn chế vận chuyển/kinh doanh hoặc hàng kinh doanh có điều kiện nhưng không cung cấp được giấy phép.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Khách hàng có nghĩa vụ mở hàng và phối hợp với Viettel Post trong việc đồng kiểm cũng như niêm phong hàng hóa khi gửi hàng.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Chịu trách nhiệm trước Viettel Post và trước pháp luật về nội dung Bưu gửi, hóa đơn, chứng từ nguồn gốc xuất xứ của Bưu gửi và chứng từ đính kèm.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Chịu trách nhiệm làm việc, giải quyết với Cơ quan có thẩm quyền khi Bưu gửi tạm giữ hoặc tịch thu.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Cung cấp đầy đủ hóa đơn, chứng từ của Bưu gửi cho Viettel Post khi gửi Bưu gửi.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Viettel Post sẽ được miễn trừ trách nhiệm bồi thường trong trường hợp Bưu gửi bị tạm giữ hoặc tịch thu bởi cơ quan có thẩm quyền do Bưu gửi không có hóa đơn, chứng từ hợp pháp đính kèm.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Đóng gói Bưu gửi theo đúng từng quy cách, kích thước và tính chất của từng mặt hàng, đặc biệt đối với Bửu gửi là các mặt hàng dễ vỡ.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Cung cấp đầy đủ chỉ dẫn liên quan đến Bưu gửi; thông tin liên quan đến Người gửi, Người nhận trên Bưu gửi.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Bồi thường thiệt hại thực tế cho Viettel Post và bên thứ 3 có liên quan khi thiệt hại xảy ra có nguồn gốc từ Khách hàng/Người gửi theo quy định của pháp luật.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Chịu trách nhiệm về mọi thông tin liên quan đến Người nhận mà Khách hàng giao cho Viettel Post. Trường hợp xảy ra sai sót về thông tin Người nhận hoặc Bưu gửi không đúng yêu cầu của Người nhận thì Khách hàng có trách nhiệm tự giải quyết với Người nhận, đồng thời Khách hàng vẫn phải thanh toán Cước phí Dịch vụ đối với Đơn hàng trên dựa trên lộ trình đã thực hiện.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Bằng chi phí của mình, chịu trách nhiệm giải quyết các vấn đề liên quan đến tranh chấp về quyền sở hữu Bưu gửi, nguồn gốc Bưu gửi với bên thứ ba bất kỳ; hoặc khiếu nại của Người nhận về việc hàng hóa bị lỗi, không đúng yêu cầu.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>Tiếp nhận và giải quyết khiếu nại Thời hiệu khiếu nại</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Bưu gửi suy suyển, hư hỏng, giá cước, nội dung khác: 01 tháng kể từ ngày bưu gửi phát thành công.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Mất mát, chuyển phát bưu gửi chậm: 06 tháng kể từ ngày kết thúc thời gian toàn trình.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– Thời gian giải quyết khiếu nại không quá 02 tháng đối với bưu gửi trong nước; không quá 03 tháng đối với bưu gửi quốc tế.</p><p style=\"text-align:justify;\">– VTP tiếp nhận, xử lý khiếu nại bằng: công văn, tổng đài 19008095, hoặc giao dịch viên trực tiếp.</p>'),(57,'PAYMENT POLICIES','internal_news','2023-06-30 08:16:07.561000','2023-08-14 01:31:12.418000','2023-06-30 08:19:51.759000',1,1,'en',NULL,'Voso.vn is an e-commerce transaction floor (referred to as “Voso.vn”) that allows organizations and individuals to buy and sell goods online. Voso.vn is built to provide domestic and international goods buying and selling application, linking with other e-commerce floors to offer many options for buyers.\n\nObjective: To become the number 1 e-commerce trading floor in Vietnam','PAYMENT POLICIES',18,0,0,'<p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;outline:none;\">Operation regulation</strong></p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Voso.vn is an e-commerce transaction floor (referred to as “Voso.vn”) that allows organizations and individuals to buy and sell goods online. Voso.vn is built to provide domestic and international goods buying and selling application, linking with other e-commerce floors to offer many options for buyers.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Objective: To become the number 1 e-commerce trading floor in Vietnam</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;outline:none;\"><i><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;outline:none;\">I. GENERAL PRINCIPLES</strong></i></em></p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">1.1. Viettel Post Joint Stock Corporation is a unit with full legal ownership and providing e-commerce services Voso.vn. Voso.vn operates on the principles of publicity, transparency, operational regulations and compliance with the law.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">1.2. This Regulation promulgates mandatory regulations applicable to members (including Merchants and Customers) wishing to trade, exchange, purchase and sell goods and provide services as well as business activities. business, trade promotion to participate on Voso.vn.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">1.3. The Seller and the Customer enter into a contract on the e-commerce floor of Voso.vn on the basis of respecting the principle of voluntary freedom, respect for the legitimate rights and interests of the parties involved in trading activities. The product is not contrary to the provisions of law.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">1.4. The purchase and sale of products and services through Voso.vn must be made openly and transparently, ensuring the interests of consumers.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">1.5. Products participating in transactions on Voso.vn are required to fully meet the provisions of relevant laws, not falling into the cases of business ban as prescribed by law.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">1.6. When selling goods on Voso.vn, sellers must find out their legal responsibilities for the current laws of Vietnam, operating regulations and other policies, regulations of Voso.vn and commitment. Links to strictly comply with relevant regulations.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">1.7. This Regulation and purchase and sale transactions on Voso.vn must always comply with the current laws of Vietnam</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;outline:none;\"><i><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;outline:none;\">II. DEFINE</strong></i></em></p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">“Voso.vn” or “E-commerce floor (or e-commerce floor) Voso.vn” is an e-commerce trading floor with the website name and domain address of Voso.vn by Viettel Post Joint Stock Corporation (VTP). ) owned. “VTP” is Viettel Post Joint Stock Corporation established and operating under the Business Registration Certificate No. 0104093672 issued by the Department of Planning and Investment of Hanoi City, registered for the first time on July 3, 2011. 2009, 15 th change registration September 20, 2018.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">“Merchants” or “Sellers” are organizations and individuals having legal business and commercial activities approved by VTP to use services provided by Voso.vn E-commerce Floor and related parties. . Through Voso.vn, the “Merchants” or “Sellers” create booths to display, introduce, buy and sell and perform other activities to buy and sell goods and services to customers.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">“Customer” or “Buyer” means organizations and individuals that buy goods and services on the e-commerce floor of Voso.vn.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">“COD” is a method of payment in cash upon receipt of goods.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">“Product” means the goods sold by the Seller through the E-commerce floor of Voso.vn.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">“Member” means Customers, Sellers who have registered accounts to use on Voso.vn.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\"><em style=\"box-sizing:border-box;outline:none;\"><i><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;font-weight:bolder;outline:none;\">III. TRANSACTION PROCESS</strong></i></em></p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">3.1. Process for Customers (Customer) When they need to buy goods on Voso.vn, the buyer will perform the following steps:</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Step 1: Search and refer to information about products, services and sellers that buyers are interested in;</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Step 2: Refer to the price information and support policies of the seller of products and services that the buyer is wishing to buy (origin, origin, quality standards, warranty …);</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Step 3: Based on the reference information from the seller of the product or service, the buyer orders and provides the receiving address information and contact the seller through the contact information posted in content of sales information to inquire about more information about products and services;</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Step 4: After providing information and making a purchase decision, the buyer can decide to order (the buyer needs to login to the member account before buying, if the buyer is not a member of the system for pre-purchase membership registration);</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Step 5: Buyers choose the method of payment, delivery and confirm “order” to complete the order.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Step 6: Buyers check the current state of goods, receive products and services;</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Step 7: Buyer inquires and complains to the seller (if any)</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">3.2. Process for Merchants To become a vendor (supplier) of products on Voso.vn, a seller will perform the following steps:</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Step 1: The seller registers the account according to the process on Voso.vn.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Step 2: Seller learns about the seller support policies and programs, select “Register”.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Step 3: Seller provides business information in the form.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Step 4: Complete the form and send it to Voso.vn.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Step 5: Voso.vn receives, checks and verifies information, the legality of the documents provided by the seller and contact the seller to verify more information, negotiate and sign the contract. providing e-commerce floor services.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">In the case that after Voso.vn checks and authenticates the information and both parties sign the contract, Voso.vn creates a booth and the Seller can post, buy and sell products posted on Voso.vn.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">3.3. Use and warranty of the product</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– The warranty policy is decided by the seller, the product buyer needs to learn carefully how to preserve the product, how long to use the product and discuss directly with the seller before buying. E-commerce platform Voso.vn only provides applications to support buying and selling.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Store the product in accordance with the supplier’s instructions.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Only use the product with expiry date.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– For food products, do not use in combination with other foods, because it can cause unhealthy reactions such as poisoning, stomachache, nausea …</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">3.4. Return / exchange policy</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Buyers and sellers communicate with each other through the information provided by the seller when posting to discuss the return of goods. Voso.vn requires the seller to specify the return policy (or not allow exchange) when posting the sale.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Voso.vn floor operates under C2C model, the sale and purchase is agreed between the buyer and the seller in a spirit of voluntariness, honesty and accuracy. To ensure honesty, objectively all goods sold on the floor must check the current state of goods, and co-check the quantity of goods by the buyer before receiving the goods. Checking the goods of the buyer must not damage or damage the manufacturer’s box and seal.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– The policy of exchange / return goods is decided by the seller and announced on the floor, the buyer needs to find out before buying. If buyers need more information, they can contact the seller to get an exact decision before buying. The purchase and sale is an independent and voluntary decision of the buyer and the seller, by the act of ordering the buyer to agree to purchase with the information provided by the seller on the floor.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">3.5. Shipping policy</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– After receiving an order from the buyer, Voso.vn will pass the information on the order to the seller and confirm the form of transportation: self-transport or hire a third party to transport.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">+ Self-transport: When a customer places an order on the system, the sales department will reconfirm the order with the customer, this confirmation via email or direct call. When reconfirming the customer about the goods, accompanying service charges if any. Customers agree, orders are ordered, packed and transferred to the sales department. Sales department receives delivery information and delivers goods to customers via motor vehicles.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">+ Hire a third party: The third party to carry out transportation is Viettel Post Corporation. When the sales team has confirmed the order with the customer, issue the order, print the order, and pass the package to the shipping partner.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">– Delivery time: Delivery time starts from the moment the order is successfully delivered by Seller to the carrier until the carrier first contacts the Buyer for delivery. The specific delivery time depends on the geographical distance between Buyer and Seller. However, Voso.vn estimates the delivery time as follows (excluding Sundays, Holidays):</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">+ Within the province: 1-2 days.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">+ Interprovincial and distance from seller to buyer less than 300 km: 2-4 days.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">+ Interprovincial and distance from seller to buyer over 300 km: 4-7 days.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Note: Some orders may take longer because Seller rescheduled the delivery for longer than expected (12 hours since bill of lading was created); or Buyer makes late delivery appointment for personal reasons.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Note: Some orders may take longer because the Seller is located in remote areas; remote or island areas.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">3.6. Order confirmation / cancellation process</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">3.6.1. Order confirmation:</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">The information stated in the Terms and Conditions and the details contained on Voso.vn are not intended to be purchased or sold but is an offer. There is no contract for any product that exists between you and Voso.vn until you receive an order confirmation or notice that the order has been shipped to your address from Voso.vn. When you submit your order request, Voso.vn will send you an order number. However, the order request needs to go through an order confirmation step in the form of a Partner or an employee of Voso.vn will call the Customer to confirm order information, personal information or delivery information. Customer’s item is correct. To request a confirmed order quickly, please provide correct and complete information regarding the delivery, or the terms and conditions of the promotion (if any) that the customer join.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">3.6.2. Cancel order:</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">If a customer makes a mistake in placing an order after confirming the order on Voso.vn, the customer should contact Customer Support immediately. Hotline: 1900-989 -888 or Email: hotro@Voso.com.vn, Voso.vn will try to process your request as soon as possible Voso.vn has the right to refuse the customer’s order for processing. anytime, anywhere, including after you have placed an order successfully. If Voso.vn cancels your order,&nbsp;the customer have paid for the order, the payment amount will be fully refunded by the payee to the customer. Voso.vn reserves the right at its sole discretion to refuse liability to the customer or any other third party for the removal of any product from Voso.vn, even if the product has been sold to the customer.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">3.7. Dispute resolution process, complaints</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Voso.vn is always responsible for receiving and handling customers’ complaints related to transactions at the e-commerce floor of Voso.vn. When any complaints and disputes arise, Voso.vn upholds the solution of negotiation and mediation between the parties in order to maintain the relationship and trust of the Customer in the service quality of Voso.vn.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">In all cases, the decision of Voso.vn is the highest and final.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">The complaint process follows these steps:</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Step 1: Customers make complaints about the Merchants purchased on the Voso.vn e-commerce floor through: Send an email to the email address: hotro@Voso.com.vn; or Call Hotline 1900 989 888; or Customer sends a complaint at the address: Viettel Post Joint Stock Corporation Address: N1 Building, Thang Long Avenue, Me Tri, Tu Liem, Hanoi</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Step 2: Customer care department will receive complaints, contact to clarify customer requirements as soon as possible and no more than 5 working days from the date of receipt of the request. Depending on the nature and severity of the incident, Voso.vn will have specific measures to assist customers in resolving complaints and disputes.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Step 3: Voso.vn may request customers and / or the Seller to provide information and evidence related to transactions and products to verify, clarify the case and take appropriate action.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Step 4: In case Voso.vn tried to resolve the complaint and dispute, but the matter is beyond its capacity and authority, Voso.vn will request the buyer to bring the case to a competent State agency for resolution. decided in accordance with the law.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Voso.vn respects and seriously implements the provisions of the law on the protection of consumers’ interests. Therefore, it is recommended that the seller on the e-commerce floor of Voso.vn provide complete, accurate, truthful and detailed information related to the product. All frauds and frauds in business are condemned and must be fully responsible before the law.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">The parties including the Seller and the Buyer play an important and responsible role in actively resolving the matter. Seller should be responsible for providing documents, documents, papers, and other evidence to prove, clarify information related to the incident that is causing conflict for the Customer. Upon request, Voso.vn will provide information relating to Buyer and Seller if agreed by such Buyer or Seller (in relation to disputes) or to the extent permitted by law. After the matter is resolved by the Buyer and the Seller, the Buyer and Seller need to report to the Voso.vn management board of the settlement results.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">In case of transactions arising from complaints and disputes, the fault of which is determined to belong to the Seller, Voso.vn will take measures to warn, close the account or transfer it to the competent State agency for handling depending on the Voso.vn will terminate and remove all articles about the Seller’s products on Voso.vn and request Seller to compensate the Customer satisfactorily on the basis of the agreement with the Customer.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">In case Voso.vn and the parties have attempted to resolve through negotiation or agreement but still cannot resolve the conflict arising from a transaction between the Customer and the Seller, either party can to bring the case to a competent State agency for settlement to ensure the legitimate interests of the parties.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-