:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Advertising with unfair competition content in accordance with the competition law.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">Advertising violates the law on intellectual property. Other acts in violation of the law on advertising. And in case the law provisions change, such changes will apply.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">8.4. The mechanism of checking and controlling product information of the Management Board of Voso.vn for products / services posted on the website:</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">The Seller sends information about the legal entity that wants to open a store on Voso.vn. After being granted an authenticated account, the Vendors can sell their products. Voso.vn will have the sole discretion to remove the Seller’s products if the products sold violate the laws, operating regulations, policies and regulations of the floor and apply penalties and claims. listed in the floor’s policies, regulations and legal regulations. Products that are not suitable for the specified category will be deleted or Voso.vn will switch to another category for it to be reasonable. Voso.vn reserves the right to decide on the storage or removal of products posted on this website without prior notice.</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">IX. LIABILITY IN CASE OF TECHNICAL ERRORS</p><p style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing:border-box;color:rgb(33, 37, 41);font-family:pfb;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin-bottom:1rem;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;outline:none;text-align:left;text-decoration-color:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;\">When m